seen the ceremony.

171
00:07:34.710 --> 00:07:38.660
(LAUGHS) I can't
think of anyone
who deserves it more.

172
00:07:38.660 --> 00:07:40.420
And as guest of honor,

173
00:07:40.461 --> 00:07:43.541
