we've never heard of?

225
00:09:44.920 --> 00:09:47.120
(CHUCKLES)
But my Dad's
heard of him.

226
00:09:47.120 --> 00:09:48.209
Yeah!

227
00:09:48.209 --> 00:09:50.119
