that require us to rise
above ourselves.

235
00:10:10.621 --> 00:10:12.539
To become better than we are.

236
00:10:12.539 --> 00:10:14.619
Ah. Thanks, Ono.

237
00:10:14.620 --> 00:10:16.580
Wise words, Hadithi.

238
00:10:16.580 --> 00:10:18.710
Indeed.

239
00:10:18.751 --> 00:10:22.041
